description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a full time highly motivated individual to join our fast-paced Endoscopy Booking Team at Harrogate Hospital.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful candidate will have experience of performing administrative and reception duties, and will be the first point of contact for patients, relatives and staff. You will admit and discharge patients following attendances, therefore waiting list experience would be desirable, but not essential. You will also have excellent communication and organisational skills and work well in a team. In addition, the individuals should be able to multi-task, prioritise own workload and meet tight deadlines. An understanding of National Waiting Time Standards and Microsoft packages would be an advantage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The role will be predominantly Monday to Friday and will be a fixed term contract for 12 months to cover for a team members maternity leave.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you have any queries about this position please contact Emma Oxtoby on 01423 557706 or at emma.oxtoby@nhs.net&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;**This job advert will close as soon as a sufficient amount of applications have been received. Please apply for this job as soon as you can, if you are interested.**&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
